===Personal pronoun===
{{rfc-header|Personal pronoun}}
# [[him]], to him (''indirect form of [[il]]'')
# [[her]], to her (''indirect form of [[elle]] before the verb'')

===Examples===
*Je '''lui''' donne un livre: I give '''him'''/'''her''' a book.
*Je donne le livre à '''lui''': I give the book to '''him'''.
*''but'' Je donne le livre à elle: I give to book to her.

